# Bancafi Saving Account Wallet

A comprehensive DeFi wallet system for managing cryptocurrency savings, earning yields, and accessing financial services.

## Architecture Overview

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     Frontend Layer                           │
│  (Web3 Integration, Wallet Connect, User Dashboard)         │
└───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘
                        │
┌───────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     API Gateway                              │
│         (Authentication, Rate Limiting, Routing)             │
└───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘
                        │
        ┌───────────────┼───────────────┐
        │               │               │
┌───────▼────────┐ ┌───▼──────────┐ ┌─▼──────────────┐
│  Wallet Service │ │ Yield Service │ │ Credit Service │
│                 │ │               │ │                │
└───────┬────────┘ └───┬──────────┘ └─┬──────────────┘
        │              │               │
        └──────────────┼───────────────┘
                       │
┌──────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────────┐
│              Smart Contract Layer                            │
│  ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐      │
│  │ Vault    │ │ Staking  │ │   SPM    │ │ Lending  │      │
│  │ Contract │ │ Contract │ │ Contract │ │ Contract │      │
│  └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘      │
└──────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┘
                       │
┌──────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────────┐
│           Blockchain Networks                                │
│  (Ethereum, BSC, Polygon, Arbitrum, etc.)                   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Project Structure

```
bancafi-wallet/
├── contracts/                 # Smart contracts
│   ├── BancafiVault.sol      # Main vault for deposits
│   ├── StakingPool.sol       # Staking and yield generation
│   ├── SPMMarker.sol         # Secure Payment Marker
│   ├── CrossChainBridge.sol  # Cross-chain functionality
│   └── LendingPool.sol       # Credit/lending collateral
├── backend/                   # Backend services
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── services/         # Business logic
│   │   ├── controllers/      # API controllers
│   │   ├── models/           # Database models
│   │   ├── middleware/       # Auth, validation
│   │   └── utils/            # Helper functions
│   └── tests/
├── scripts/                   # Deployment scripts
├── docs/                      # Documentation
└── tests/                     # Contract tests
```

## Core Features

### 1. Secure Deposits
- Multi-signature security
- Smart contract-based custody
- Time-lock mechanisms for large withdrawals

### 2. Interest Earnings
- Dynamic APY based on market conditions
- Auto-compounding options
- Multiple staking tiers

### 3. Cross-Chain Support
- LayerZero integration for seamless transfers
- Support for ETH, BSC, Polygon, Arbitrum
- Unified balance view across chains

### 4. SPM Integration
- Transaction verification
- Fraud prevention
- Audit trail for compliance

### 5. Automated Savings
- Scheduled deposits
- Goal-based savings tracking
- Dollar-cost averaging strategies

### 6. Credit Services
- Collateralized lending
- Dynamic LTV ratios
- Liquidation protection

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Node.js >= 18.x
- Hardhat
- PostgreSQL
- Redis

### Installation

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Compile contracts
npx hardhat compile

# Run tests
npx hardhat test

# Deploy contracts
npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network <network>

# Start backend
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Security Features

- Multi-signature wallets for large operations
- Time-locked withdrawals
- Rate limiting and circuit breakers
- Regular security audits
- Emergency pause functionality

